headline: Blue Owl Capital (OWL) Surges 14.3%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Blue Owl Capital (OWL) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
